File: internal/client/providers/grpc/info_client.go
Package: grpc
Role: Infrastructure Transport Adapter
Purpose: Connects to remote storage nodes over secure TLS channels to query server operational state parameters.

Functions:
func FetchServerInfo(ctx context.Context, serverAddr string) (*pb.InfoResponse, error). Purpose: communication logic. Resolves client TLS properties, boots non-blocking grpc.NewClient, sets isolated 5-second context timeouts, triggers Remote Procedure Call. Errors: wrapped TLS setup, connection, or remote status failure.

